verbose_text: Overexpression of mul1 or park in neurons of flies fed with rotenone, reversed this result and increased climbing by up to 70 and 60% in elav> mul1 and elav> park, respectively, compared with the control strains (elav-Gal4 and UAS-mul1 for elav> mul1 and elav-Gal4 and UAS-park for elav> park) (p < 0.001).
evidence: mul1 or park in neurons of flies fed with rotenone, reversed this result
